---
title: Hawaiian Pizzettes with Fries & Salad
description: Pineapple on a pizzette? It's a big YES from us with this fun fusion that has traditional Italian flavours meeting Modern. Juicy, sweet pineapple and smokey ham are the fundamentals of a classic Hawaiian - top it off with a melty duo of Cheddar and Parmesan and you'll be saying "Aloha!" to your new go-to pizza dinner.
